all the files are stored inside /opt/docker
creating user ansadmin user and  is added to docker group
changing permsission to the folder /opt/docker to ansadmin user
sudo chown -R ansadmin:ansadmin /opt/docker
ansible will create the docker images on ansible host and publish it to docker host orelse any target server
ssh is established between ansadmin user and localhost so that it will save images on ansible host
ssh-copy-id localhost
